{"type":"message","id":"f5f21b71","parentId":"4b1418d9","timestamp":"2026-04-27T21:04:43.480Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Let me check the iCloud emails more carefully. The envelopes with \"!\" flag are marked urgent/important. Let me read the iCloud emails to get summaries. The timestamps are in UTC, so let me convert:\n- Email 9: 2026-04-27 19:06 UTC = 3:06 PM EDT\n- Email 8: 2026-04-27 12:20 UTC = 8:20 AM EDT\n\nFor Gmail:\n1. Aventine Northshore - Pay your rent online using a mobile device (Promotions)\n2. Apotheca - Don't Miss Out on PuffCo Savings! 💨 (Promotions)\n\n\n3. TikTok - ari: no way that was 3 years ago💔 (Updates)\n\nNone of these appear urgent, so I'll send both reports now.","thinkingSignature":"e67323558b5194155db0275e63d2b80a2633a291ae01353d278f8e19851afa16"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2wb82em5pxo0_1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"himalaya message read 9 --account icloud 2>&1 | grep -v WARN | head -30"}},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_2wb82em5pxo0_2","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"himalaya message read 8 --account icloud 2>&1 | grep -v WARN | head -30"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1148,"output":262,"cacheRead":19036,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20446,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777323876589,"responseId":"063f026451d4069587108b9e6f8bfdef"}}
{"type":"message","id":"78ab60f4","parentId":"f5f21b71","timestamp":"2026-04-27T21:04:45.030Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2wb82em5pxo0_1","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"From: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHello,\n\nOk sounds good. I may have one for that time frame. Just keep in mind they are first come first serve. Once approved, your application stays with us until we can link you to a unit. Once Logan is done, we can begin the process. Any questions feel free to reach out.\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Monday, April 27, 2026 12:17 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1131,"aggregated":"From: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nHello,\n\nOk sounds good. I may have one for that time frame. Just keep in mind they are first come first serve. Once approved, your application stays with us until we can link you to a unit. Once Logan is done, we can begin the process. Any questions feel free to reach out.\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Monday, April 27, 2026 12:17 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777323885030}}
{"type":"message","id":"b3ea3ae4","parentId":"78ab60f4","timestamp":"2026-04-27T21:04:45.031Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_2wb82em5pxo0_2","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"From: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1533,"aggregated":"From: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nTo: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment\n\nGood Morning,\n\nOnce Logan completes his, I can run the apps. When are you looking to move by so I can make sure I will have one Available?\n\n\nAmy Smith\n\nLeasing Agent\n\nT  |  845.452.3450 x312\nE  |  RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com<mailto:RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\n\nW | royalcoveapts.com\n\n\n\n[A picture containing text, font, screenshot, graphics  Description automatically generated]\n\n\n\n________________________________\nFrom: rtg.bobby@icloud.com <rtg.bobby@icloud.com>\nSent: Saturday, April 25, 2026 1:49 PM\nTo: RC Leasing <RCLeasing@lexingtonpg.com>\nSubject: Re: Looking for new apartment","cwd":"/Users/bobbygalletta/.openclaw/workspace-emmy"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1777323885030}}
{"type":"message","id":"dc69674f","parentId":"b3ea3ae4","timestamp":"2026-04-27T21:04:56.174Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have enough info. Let me compose both messages.\n\nGmail - 3 new emails, all low priority:\n1. Aventine Northshore - Pay your rent online using a mobile device (Promotions)\n2. Apotheca - Don't Miss Out on PuffCo Savings! 💨 (Promotions)\n3. TikTok - ari: no way that was 3 years ago💔 (Updates)\n\niCloud - 2 new emails:\n1. RC Leasing (email 9) - Re: Looking for new apartment - about moving process, Logan needs to complete something. This seems like important/personal.\n2. \n\nRC Leasing (email 8) - Re: Looking for new apartment - asking when Bobby is looking to move by. Also important/personal.\n\nThe iCloud emails are from the last hour, so they're definitely new. Let me send the messages now.","thinkingSignature":"108be082771a16d89c191c1fa959fe1b6d4a2cbafd5030e498eac3c26c7e95d8"},{"type":"text","text":"📬 **GMAIL — New Mail (3 new)**\n\n⚪ LOW PRIORITY:\n• Aventine Northshore — Pay your rent online using a mobile device\n  └ Promotional reminder to pay rent via mobile\n\n• Apotheca — Don't Miss Out on PuffCo Savings! 💨\n  └ Sale/promotion for PuffCo products\n\n• TikTok — ari: no way that was 3 years ago🥲💔\n  └ TikTok newsletter/personal post notification\n\n---\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_oqmxzg1vwcvf_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","channel":"telegram","target":"8212808444","message":"📬 ICLOUD — New Mail (2 new)\n\n🟡 IMPORTANT:\n• RC Leasing (Amy Smith) — Re: Looking for new apartment\n  └ Amy says she may have a unit for your timeframe; waiting on Logan to complete his application before running the process ⚠️\n\n• RC Leasing (Amy Smith) — Re: Looking for new apartment\n  └ Amy asking when you're looking to move by so she can ensure availability ⚠️"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":1865,"output":441